OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FQuite cloudy at first around
OL,6,Fnorthern counties but bright with a
OL,7,Ffew sunny spells elsewhere. Remaining
OL,8,Fdry and very warm with good sunny
OL,9,Fspells and variable cloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight with evening
OL,13,Fsunshine and then clear spells, and
OL,14,Fvariable amounts of cloud.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FSunny spells and variable
OL,17,Fcloud at first. Cloud will break up to
OL,18,Fleave good prolonged sunny spells
OL,19,Fthrough the day and feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
